{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/nosurrender/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"2bb377bf-d3fa-56b6-b4a6-8901edb1ecde","html":"<p class=\"align-center\">\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://work.joanmira.com/webs/nosurrender/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived website without DB</a>\n</p>\n<p>No Surrender contacted me to build an online shop to sell their products. They wanted a very personal style combined with great UX and an easy payment method.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 35%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/3371ec26fad6b9ba0d8a617e9f25bc11/dbdff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3371ec26fad6b9ba0d8a617e9f25bc11/d1f95/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/3371ec26fad6b9ba0d8a617e9f25bc11/dbdff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>I used TIENDAFlash, the software that I previously created for another customer that required a Flash online shop. TIENDAFlash is a Flash + PHP + MySQL solution that allows the maximum flexibility in the front-end and a very compatible and extended tech stack for the backend. It also features a custom CMS to add/edit/remove products, categories, photos and customers. I also implemented a credit/debit card payment gateway using the API from ServiRed (a very popular banking network in Spain).</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1064px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/aeb1b92ab9eb5f611168c5e5293e6e2e/1fe61/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aeb1b92ab9eb5f611168c5e5293e6e2e/d1f95/2.jpg 500w,\n/static/aeb1b92ab9eb5f611168c5e5293e6e2e/dbdff/2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/aeb1b92ab9eb5f611168c5e5293e6e2e/1fe61/2.jpg 1064w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1064px) 100vw, 1064px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1064px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"3\"\n        src=\"/static/9c679189c670fc44ebb7b819c923b65b/1fe61/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9c679189c670fc44ebb7b819c923b65b/d1f95/3.jpg 500w,\n/static/9c679189c670fc44ebb7b819c923b65b/dbdff/3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/9c679189c670fc44ebb7b819c923b65b/1fe61/3.jpg 1064w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1064px) 100vw, 1064px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; mar